snippet.title: Amber Heard WRECKS HERSELF after LASHING OUT because LOSING! OOPS!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard WRECKS HERSELF after LASHING OUT because LOSING! OOPS!

On the face of it, the media treats this as a win for Amber Heard. BUT it looks like a BIG mistake considering this goes both ways! See, this opens a doorway for "turnabout," which would examine some of the things she and her side have done. And there is PROOF of wrongdoing, which I added here!
